1. download a tesseract version from here
    >> https://github.com/UB-Mannheim/tesseract/wiki
2. add this line to your code
    >> pt.pytesseract.tesseract_cmd = r"C:\Program Files (x86)\Tesseract-OCR\tesseract.exe"
where the sting in "" means the location where you have installed the tesseract-ocr
3. goto your cmd and type
    >> pip install pytesseract
4. add the installation address of tesseract-ocr in system variable. To do this follow the steps:
    >> right clcik 'This Pc' on desktop and click on 'properties'. Then click on 'Advance System Settings'.
    then click on 'Environment Variable' to the bottom right corner. Then click on 'Path' in System Variable and click
    'New'. Then copy the tesseract Installation location and paste there.